data.description: Enjoy this end unit townhouse featuring a tankless water heater, surround sound speakers, walk in master closet, stainless steel appliances… First floor room can either be used as a bedroom or family room with a connecting bath. Amenities include a Spacious Clubhouse with lake and pool views, Resort-style pool with waterslide, beach-like entrance, splash park, lap lanes, cabanas, and abundant deck space. 3 naturally stocked lakes. Lake piers/overlooks. Miles of nature trails. Large playground. Home to be sold with minimal to no repairs.
